commit.message:
Introduce a simple Dockerfile

This Dockerfile allows for building off of certbot's official
Docker image while adding the lets-do-dns program as present
in this repository. While we're at it, we'll use this new Dockerfile
to test out full functionality with the certbot program through the
Jenkinsfile build script.
